These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, cabbage, carrot, garlic
House: townhouse, futuristic, ranch-style, colonial
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, epic, family, romance
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, d&b, dubstep, electronic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, swimming, water-polo, snowboarding
 1. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
 2. the futuristic house is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 3. the colonial house is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 5. the fan of classical is the person eating asparagus##1
 6. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 7. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the person eating carrot is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 9. the person watching family movies is the person eating asparagus##1
10. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person watching epic movies##1
11. the townhouse house is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | cabbage    | carrot      | asparagus  | garlic     |
| House         | colonial    | ranch-style   | townhouse | futuristic      |
| Movie-Genre   | epic       | documentary | family     | romance    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | d&b         | classical  | dubstep    |
| Sport           | water-polo      | snowboarding       | surfing | swimming |

