.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, fanta, hot-chocolate
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, satire, spy
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, bluemaster, siglo, tiparillo
House: cottage, palace, colonial, art-deco
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, handball, parkour, skiing
 1. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 8. the palace house is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is the siglo-smoker##1
10. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | coffee      | 7up     | fanta    | hot-chocolate |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | drama   | satire   | spy           |
| Cigar   | bluemaster  | tiparillo     | siglo    | ritmeester         |
| House           | art-deco         | palace | colonial     | cottage        |
| Sport         | cricket     | skiing  | handball | parkour       |

