.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, cauliflower, grapes, lettuce
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, fantasy, documentary, thriller
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, mouse, rabbit
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, january, july, december
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, subway, tram, trike
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 3. the person eating grapes is the owner of the rabbit##1
 4. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 6. the person driving the trike is the person eating grapes##1
 7. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 8. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 9. the person watching thriller movies is the owner of the frog##1
10. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
11. the person driving the trike is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
12. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Food          | cabbage    | lettuce      | grapes  | cauliflower   |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller     | documentary      | fantasy | family      |
| Pet           | frog       | fish         | rabbit  | mouse         |
| Birthday         | may | january | july  | december |
| Transport     | tram       | bike         | trike   | subway        |

