.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, skateboarding, parkour, basketball
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, drawing, gardening, skydiving
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, journalist, musician, teacher
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, canadian, spanish, turkish
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, march, september, october
 1. the dancer is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left##1
 3. the canadian is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 6. the musician is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is the dancer##1
 9. the person who's sport is basketball is the person who's birthday is in september##1
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
11. the australian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
12. the journalist is on the far left##1
13. the australian is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
14. the spanish is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Sport          | cricket       | skateboarding     | parkour     | basketball  |
| Hobby         | gardening  | skydiving | collecting | drawing  |
| Job           | journalist | dancer    | teacher    | musician |
