 3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 5. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
 6. the person who likes yellow is on the far left##1
 7. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 8. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is the person driving the subway##1
10. the person drinking water is the owner of the dog##1
11. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who likes white##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Beverage    | coffee     | hot-chocolate  | water       | mirinda      |
| Color       | yellow    | light-blue        | grey  | white      |
| Cigar         | havana  | pall-mall | davidoff | vegafina |
| Pet         | chinchilla | mouse          | dog         | hamster      |
| Transport   | subway     | helicopter     | trike       | van          |

